  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/761",
  "title": "[Pagination] when maxPage is not specified it's set to 20",
  "body": "```\nsearch.addWidget(\n  instantsearch.widgets.pagination({\n    container: '#pagination-container',\n    scrollTo: false\n  })\n);\n```\n\nWill limit the number of page to 20, this is really weird\n\nI think it is ok to document it like this\n\n```\nsearch.addWidget(\n  instantsearch.widgets.pagination({\n    container: '#pagination-container',\n    maxPages: 20,\n    scrollTo: false\n  })\n);\n```\n\nbut removing the param should not let the 20 pages limit\n",
